bodies.description:
{color: #FF9900}Card Tag System
{color}{color: #80B3FF}Trident Mobile{color} will enable card tags permanently while being
used. The reason for this is because {color: #9933FF}Ghost Cards{color} are also
Locked Units with your{color: #33CC33} Real Units{color}. So to help users differentiate
their{color: #33CC33} 'Real'{color} cards from their{color: #9933FF} 'Ghosts'{color} cards, there is a custom{color: #FF0000}
Tag System{color} in place with{color: #80B3FF} Trident{color} where{color: #FF0000} Card Tag #1{color} are your{color: #33CC33}
'Real' cards{color} and {color: #FF0000} Card Tag #2{color} are your{color: #9933FF} 'Ghost' cards{color}. This will
not overwrite your tags you had. This change is only when
using{color: #80B3FF} Trident Mobile{color}. Users can not edit tags while using{color: #80B3FF}
Trident Mobile{color}, as it is just a safety precaution.
